metadata.name: Ancient God of the Forest I
metadata.description:
The first of a series between 10 and 15 1/1 final pieces of Ancient Gods of the Forest. 

Inspired by mythology, celtic gods, other deities and the wonders of nature.  I wanted to represent beauty, power, elegance and the fragility of our surroundings.  

All hand hand drawn with pen & ink taking well over 50 hrs per drawing.

Each collector will receive a special air dropped edition of the final God once the collection is complete.

4006 x 5060 px
